text: The 2015 Walsall Metropolitan Borough Council election took place on 7 May 2015 to elect members of Walsall Metropolitan Borough Council in England. This was on the same day as other local elections. ==Council make up== After the 2015 local election, the political make up of the council was as follows: {| class="wikitable" |- ! Party !!
